Invocation Name: twin cities transit
des:
Use this skill to get the next bus times for metro transit bus stops.

If you don't know your stop number, each bus stop has a sign post, this has a stop number on it. Now that you have the stop number, you can say "Check stop <insert-stop-number-here>.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
